aaj phir jeene ki tamanna hai
mujhe chhoo rahi hain teri garam
ho gaya hai tujhko to pyaar sajnaa
hum ne sanam ko khat likha
dil mein ho tum aankhon mein
kisi raah mein kis mod pe
aankhon mein neenden na dil mein karaar
hum teri mohabbat mein yun pagal
kahin pe nigahen kahin pe nishana
chehra hai ya chaand khila hai
kahin door jab din dhal jaaye
bin tere sanam mar mitenge hum
pahle kabhi na mera haal aisa
kahin na jaa aaj kahin mat jaa
tumse mil ke aisa laga tumse mil ke
yeh samaa samaa hai yeh pyaar ka
